              Extra pale ale kit (Nugget hops) with additional Cascade hops during primary. Stayed super clean during all processes and ended up with great results - clear amber body and creamy billowing head.  It has been about 50 days since primary fermentation and it tastes better each successive week.<br /><br /><img src="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/2334983/homebrew02.jpg" alt="Image" /><br /><br /><img src="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/2334983/homebrew01.jpg" alt="Image" /><br /><br />Next up is a double IPA!

              

              
              
